\Gamma(iy)\,\Gamma(-iy)=|\Gamma(iy)|^2=\frac{\pi}{y\,\sinh(\pi y)}
\Gamma(x+iy)\approx (iy)^x\,\Gamma(iy)\quad\text{for}\ |x|\ll |y|
